---
title: Garlic-Herb Chicken & Pumpkin Freekeh with Tahini & Yoghurt Sauce
description: Add tonnes of flavour to your dinner with our garlic and herb seasoning! Here we've used it to coat succulent chicken
strips, served with roasted veggies and freekeh. It's definitely a meal to remember!

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with freekeh due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
